name: CI Global Longevity Economy Fund
longDescription: The funds objective is to obtain maximum long-term capital growth by investing primarily in equity and equity-related securities of companies throughout the world thatthe portfolio advisor believes are well-positioned to benefit from an ageing population, increasing life expectancy, increasing lifestyle expenditures and evolvingdemographic needs worldwide. the portfolio advisor believes are well-positioned to benefit from an ageing population, increasing life expectancy, increasing lifestyle expenditures and evolvingdemographic needs worldwide.
